Subject: What's New in KDE 5
Description: The KDE project has released Plasma 5, and with it comes many changes. Come learn what's new in this latest popular open source desktop environment. Whether you're already a KDE user, or just curious about desktops, you will learn something as we run down what's new with an eye to the past. We will also spend some time contrasting the desktop to its competition in Unity and Gnome.  Speakers include:Ryan Kather - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector

Subject: Understanding and Protecting Your Privacy Online
Description: Everyday it seems more of our daily lives are intertwined with our online identities, and yet it seems that there is ever less privacy online. Come learn how interested parties are monitoring you online, what drives their motivations, and steps you can take to mitigate your private information exposure.  Speakers include:Ryan Kather - Track: Tech  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: Projector
